msg: Fix a few minor bugs found during dav tests of r17708.
(svn_ebcdic_run_unix_type_script): Don't convert err_stream to utf-8, leave
it native so it better parallels the behavior of svn_stringbuf_from_aprfile
and svn_io_wait_for_cmd as used in hooks.c's run_hook_cmd.
(test_tempdir, svn_io_temp_dir): Revert r17496, the iSeries needs this
as IBM's apr_temp_dir_get still doesn't work.
(dav_svn__merge_response): Use APR_PSPRINTF in place of apr_psprintf so
post_commit_header_info is ebcdic encoded despite a utf-8 variable arg.
